WEBVTT

00:00:00.160 --> 00:00:06.696
Good morning, family. How are y'all doing today? I have some things on my heart, but first off, let's give God some praise.

00:00:06.697 --> 00:00:29.465
For the Lord is good and his mercy endures forever. Father, I thank you that you endure forever and your mercy is new every morning.

00:00:29.466 --> 00:00:35.656
Great is your faithfulness to me, oh God. Thank you, Father, for all that you're going to do today.

00:00:35.657 --> 00:00:42.017
I ask you, Father, to anoint this broadcast, this video today, and this YouTube video.

00:00:42.017 --> 00:00:46.354
I thank you, Father, that you speak through my vocal cords and you think through my mind.

00:00:46.355 --> 00:00:51.832
None of me and all of you, in the mighty name of Jesus. I thank you, Father.

00:00:51.833 --> 00:01:02.072
I have an urgency in my heart for what's coming and to tell the people that Jesus is coming.

00:01:02.073 --> 00:01:14.443
Well, this is what I have for y'all today. I was driving down the road and the Lord just decided to speak. I mean, the prophetic unction just hit me hard.

00:01:14.444 --> 00:01:27.039
Like I said, I do not consider myself a prophet, but when I pray, I see visions and the Lord shows me things to come.

00:01:27.040 --> 00:01:35.056
He showed me Israel, and I saw a major event about to take place in Israel.

00:01:35.057 --> 00:01:43.393
I saw at this time people in the streets with prayer shawls like what I have.

00:01:43.394 --> 00:01:57.199
They had these prayer things, they had the Israeli flag, and they had it over their shoulders, kind of like what they do at a sporting event, but they had it like this and it was draped around them.

00:01:57.200 --> 00:02:03.673
They were celebrating in the streets, saying, "The deliverer has come.

00:02:03.674 --> 00:02:14.083
The deliverer has come."The women were dancing in the streets and the men were dancing, and they were celebrating some kind of victory.

00:02:14.084 --> 00:02:27.113
I do not know what this was, if it was war or whatever. All I know is they were celebrating something that had happened in the streets in Israel.

00:02:27.114 --> 00:02:44.258
I saw rabbis. I saw Orthodox Jews with their hats on with curls and long beards, and they were weeping at this sight, at this experience.

00:02:44.259 --> 00:02:58.559
They were rocking at the Wailing Wall. I could see them praying and weeping at the Wailing Wall, and I could see them throughout the streets. I saw them actually say, "We've been in error.

00:02:58.560 --> 00:03:18.551
We have been in error in some of our teachings."The Holy Spirit had gotten a hold of them and they were telling the people—I saw them teaching and telling the people that they had been in error about some things and they were going back and correcting things that they had been teaching that were in error.

00:03:18.552 --> 00:03:32.930
I saw a glory explosion over the Jewish people. A mighty revival started to break out in the streets in Jerusalem and all of the other areas of Israel.

00:03:32.931 --> 00:03:41.566
They were breaking forth in a revival of healings and demonstrations and manifestations of the glory.

00:03:41.567 --> 00:03:54.608
And the Lord said, "I'm going to become real to this generation like I had been in the past with the children of Israel when they were delivered out of the hand of Egypt.

00:03:54.609 --> 00:04:22.991
I'm going to do another wave of my presence, of my glory, over this generation, and they will see that I am real and that I am their Messiah, that I am God to them."The Lord showed me a great and mighty wave of his presence over all of the people.

00:04:22.992 --> 00:04:37.328
But they were delivered from something. Like I said, I do not know what this was about, but they were dancing in the streets. I could see the rabbis and the tears that were flowing.

00:04:37.329 --> 00:04:47.918
There was a heavy-set man, and I don't know who this man was, but he had chubbier, heavier cheeks and a longer, silvery-peppered beard.

00:04:47.919 --> 00:04:54.333
I could see gray in his beard. He was a rabbi, and he had glasses on and he was rocking.

00:04:54.334 --> 00:05:03.973
I remember seeing these curls, but I could see the people and they were teaching that "we were erring in our ways,"and they knew that they were corrected about some things.

00:05:03.974 --> 00:05:18.319
I just thought it was amazing in this visitation. The Lord just told me that he was going to become real, and I don't want to keep rehashing that, but I'm just going back over my mind, remembering everything I was shown.

00:05:18.320 --> 00:05:42.715
Then the Lord showed me this. He said, "Brandon, I'm going to uncap the wells of revival in America."And he said to me, "The great healing revivals that took place in the 1930s and 40s—you know, the tent revivals back whenever A.

00:05:42.716 --> 00:05:53.998
A. Allen, Jack Coe, William Branham, Smith, not Kenneth Hagin, but you know, John G.

00:05:53.999 --> 00:06:00.484
Lake, that era of ministers."He told me Aimee Semple McPherson, and it goes on and on.

00:06:00.485 --> 00:06:06.292
He said, "Those wells were capped."People have wondered, "Where has that gone?"They were capped.

00:06:06.293 --> 00:06:12.213
I looked up what the word 'capped'means. What does it mean to cap a well?

00:06:12.214 --> 00:06:30.328
The wells that are no longer being used but might be needed in the future can be sealed with a cap that covers the top of the well casing pipe to prevent unauthorized access and contamination.

00:06:30.329 --> 00:06:39.289
A cap is a temporary groundwater protection solution that allows a well to be used at a later time.

00:06:39.290 --> 00:07:00.125
He brought up the scripture in Genesis and he was talking about Isaac bringing forth the old wells that Abraham had dug, that the Philistines put dirt on and filled up, and capped those wells off.

00:07:00.126 --> 00:07:09.279
But the Lord was showing me that he's uncapping those wells of revival.

00:07:09.280 --> 00:07:29.288
He's uncapping all those deep wells. I was driving by Tulsa, ORU, and I saw the glory. I started crying again.

00:07:29.289 --> 00:07:53.191
I saw the glory over the Mabee Center, and I saw the glory of the Lord over there again, and those old wells of revival from Oral Roberts and the greats that walked this land before and have gone home to be with the Lord.

00:07:53.192 --> 00:08:19.270
He said, "I'm going to do it one more time, and I'm bringing forth a great revival again, son."Those old wells that have been capped for protection because the season was over for that, he said, "I'm bringing forth those great wells again, and I'm going to use you and I'm going to use these people for great healings.

00:08:19.271 --> 00:08:23.905
Demonstrations and manifestations of my glory will be seen again.

00:08:23.906 --> 00:08:32.390
I'm going to touch this generation one more time."I told you, he said, "There's one more call.

00:08:32.391 --> 00:08:38.551
One last call."And I've asked him because people were arguing with me and saying, "Oh, there's no great revival.

00:08:38.552 --> 00:08:53.309
That's not in the Bible in the last days."Well, I was out there and I said, "Lord, what do you say to this?"And he said, "Brandon, who's in control of time?"He said, "I am.

00:08:53.310 --> 00:09:09.919
Were you there when I threw the stars into space? Were you there when I created the heavens and the earth?"He was referring to Job whenever he was talking to Job.

00:09:09.920 --> 00:09:19.999
He said, "Brandon, my heart is the harvest. My heart is the harvest.

00:09:20.000 --> 00:09:27.275
One last call, son. I'm calling in the sheep from the back of the fold. One last call.

00:09:27.276 --> 00:09:38.719
I'm calling them forth to come home, giving them an opportunity."And in this, I'm going to uncap those great wells of revival.

00:09:38.720 --> 00:09:48.872
And I saw at this time a vision of tents full of people again. I saw tents and brush harbor churches again.

00:09:48.873 --> 00:10:00.559
He showed me a revival of fire like what Azusa Street had. I'm so hungry for this.

00:10:00.560 --> 00:10:31.119
The glorious church in Collinsville, Oklahoma—he's going to use this place.

00:10:31.120 --> 00:10:34.271
He's going to use Branson, Missouri. He's going to use these places.

00:10:34.272 --> 00:10:55.498
And he told me, "Those that are hungry and thirsty after righteousness, they will be filled with my glory."He said, "I want you to go back and I want to speak to you about Rosh Hashanah to Rosh Hashanah."This time, he said, "This is the beginning of the glory.

00:10:55.499 --> 00:11:09.982
This is the beginning of what you have waited for for so long."He talked about a great harvest of souls coming from Rosh Hashanah to Rosh Hashanah.

00:11:09.983 --> 00:11:14.716
You will see first the blade, then the ear, and then the corn.

00:11:14.717 --> 00:11:33.018
Concerning this, the greater harvest of the glory that you have wanted for so long will come: first the blade, then the ear, and then the full corn. You will see it.

00:11:33.019 --> 00:11:56.532
He said, "This is a time of refreshing, a time of surrender, a time of rest, a time of healing, a period to fully let go and prepare for the new cycle ahead."He talked about the Democratic Party and the evil over the United States of America.

00:11:56.533 --> 00:12:12.239
There will be an event that will shake the USA out of a fear to control; they will lose control, is what the Lord said.

00:12:12.240 --> 00:12:24.638
He said seedtime and harvest will have come to its fullest. You will see this happen.

00:12:24.639 --> 00:12:32.503
Seedtime and harvest will come to its fullest in these days ahead.

00:12:32.504 --> 00:12:44.509
The seeds they have sowed in the past will come to harvest finally at last. Then he started talking to me about a great humbling.

00:12:44.510 --> 00:12:52.423
A great humbling will come, an uprising; there will be weeping, and they will be very sad.

00:12:52.424 --> 00:13:08.393
People will say, "What did we do?"You will see an exposing of great darkness in the Democratic Party.

00:13:08.394 --> 00:13:16.280
And when this happens, the very snake they thought they controlled will turn on them.

00:13:16.281 --> 00:13:28.209
I saw that big python that I told you all about in the past lashing out, striking, striking, striking.

00:13:28.210 --> 00:13:37.688
It was striking them. I saw an exposing. I saw embarrassing moments coming from Kamala Harris.

00:13:37.689 --> 00:13:47.070
I saw things that were done in the past that she thought she had buried and were no longer a problem resurfacing.

00:13:47.071 --> 00:14:04.713
There were several incidents of things that were dirty, things that were very embarrassing to the point where I heard her saying, "I should have never ran.

00:14:04.714 --> 00:14:12.074
I should have never put my foot in this,"because they were very humiliating.

00:14:12.075 --> 00:14:20.594
I saw very humiliating things coming, things that were not meant to be, and people leaked it.

00:14:20.595 --> 00:14:25.754
There is corruption on the Republican side and the Democratic side.

00:14:25.755 --> 00:14:40.076
People think the Republicans are sanctimonious folks, but there is corruption on the Democrats and corruption on the Republicans, and there are going to be exposings.

00:14:40.077 --> 00:14:49.078
I saw women and different ethnic groups that had blinders on their eyes.

00:14:49.079 --> 00:14:58.554
When these things start to manifest, the blinders will fall off. I saw them becoming enlightened.

00:14:58.555 --> 00:15:07.518
It was similar to whenever you see somebody that's bewitched; they have a spell over them and they don't even realize it.

00:15:07.519 --> 00:15:25.460
They have a demonic band wrapped around their mind. I saw a breaking of this and them being set free. Their minds became enlightened.

00:15:25.461 --> 00:15:35.263
When this happens, they will be furious because the eyes of their understanding were enlightened, Ephesians 1:18.

00:15:35.264 --> 00:15:40.212
There will be people who want to have lynch mobs, rioting, and pillaging.

00:15:40.213 --> 00:15:51.607
They will be upset about how they were lied to because the darkness they tried to deceive everyone with will come out into the open.

00:15:51.608 --> 00:15:56.559
They will not be able to hide from the things that they have sown.

00:15:56.560 --> 00:16:02.539
There was an exposing in the financial realm and the natural realm.

00:16:02.540 --> 00:16:11.425
You will see it. Watch this. I saw Jerome Powell again, and I saw him taking Jenga pieces.

00:16:11.426 --> 00:16:29.174
I saw a great Jenga tower. I saw him pulling from the middle of the Jenga tower. He was watching as he pulled to see if it would fall.

00:16:29.175 --> 00:16:34.615
All of a sudden, I saw the vision going straight to the middle of the Jenga tower.

00:16:34.616 --> 00:16:40.165
All the tower was built up, but in the middle there was no foundation.

00:16:40.166 --> 00:16:50.561
It was only on one block, and that block fell and all of it crumbled. It was awful. Everybody was panicking.

00:16:50.562 --> 00:17:03.296
I saw Wall Street and the day traders panicking, selling and selling. It was chaos in Wall Street. Everybody was freaking out.

00:17:03.297 --> 00:17:11.122
I could see the storm over New York and the Lord showed me great darkness.

00:17:11.123 --> 00:17:28.798
But then he said to me, "Everything will change in a 24-hour period."It will be just like that, similar to how 9/11 took place.

00:17:28.799 --> 00:17:37.809
It will be a lot like what happened with 9/11. I saw a change of things happening in a 24-hour period.

00:17:37.810 --> 00:17:44.879
Everything that was would be no more. A change that happens that fast.

00:17:44.880 --> 00:17:53.948
I don't know when this takes place, but when it does, it will change everything within a 24-hour period.

00:17:53.949 --> 00:18:07.992
I saw the wealth of the sinner laid up for the righteous. I saw a great supernatural harvest of finances.

00:18:07.993 --> 00:18:17.882
When this takes place, it will be similar to the children of Israel leaving Egypt and getting the wealth from the Egyptians.

00:18:17.883 --> 00:18:26.514
This will be a type and shadow of what God is going to do in this generation before he takes us out with the rapture of the church.

00:18:26.515 --> 00:18:35.008
We will have the wealth of the sinner laid up for the righteous. The Lord said it will be a type and shadow of this event.

00:18:35.009 --> 00:18:45.970
God said, "I will provide for my beloved."I was talking about the major churches that are in compromise.

00:18:45.971 --> 00:19:08.888
If you are writing worship music to try to get a Dove Award or clout for finances concerning the glory outpouring, or preaching the gospel on a YouTube channel always asking for money because you're touching God's anointing, you're in trouble.

00:19:08.889 --> 00:19:18.719
You will wake up and your channel will be gone that fast because God said, "Touch not my anointed."Watch what happens to you.

00:19:18.720 --> 00:19:29.860
I don't care if you're trying to sell a book, but if your whole mission is to make profit off of the body of Christ, you're in trouble.

00:19:29.861 --> 00:19:37.578
Woe unto you. If you're writing a book to help people, I get it; there are costs with it.

00:19:37.579 --> 00:19:46.555
But if you're writing a book or a song for worship just for material gain, woe unto you.

00:19:46.556 --> 00:19:53.652
He told me, "Brandon, never go on the platform and ever ask for a dime from my people.

00:19:53.653 --> 00:20:01.024
Not one time."He said if I make a video trying to make profit, the channel will be no more.

00:20:01.025 --> 00:20:04.657
He'll take the anointing off the channel and it will be done.

00:20:04.658 --> 00:20:14.462
You want to know why your channels aren't growing? It's because you're trying to profit off of God's people.

00:20:14.463 --> 00:20:23.180
God says there is coming an end to that. If you feed the sheep, God said he would feed you.

00:20:23.181 --> 00:20:42.837
But if your heart is just to make money off of God's people, woe unto you; those seasons are done. God's drawing a line in the sand.

00:20:42.838 --> 00:20:54.672
You'll see the wolves among the sheep, and you're going to be able to see the ones that are called to God because the light's going to get brighter and the darkness is going to get darker.

00:20:54.673 --> 00:21:06.404
And you're going to see the ones that are false and the ones that are right, because the righteous are going to rise up with the glory of the Lord and the manifestations of His presence beyond anything you've ever seen before.

00:21:06.405 --> 00:21:13.999
And you're going to look at the ones that have been on Daystar and the ones that have been on these other channels, and you're going to go, 'Who are they?

00:21:14.000 --> 00:21:31.584
What happened to them?'And you're going to say, 'What happened to their ministry?'Because it's all going to fall because they are all seeking after material gain, their own popularity, and their own position, trying to uplift themselves because they wanted man's praise and approval.

00:21:31.585 --> 00:21:41.599
But God's calling forth a people like David that will go in and cut the head off the giant and don't need any praise because we're always looking to give Him the praise.

00:21:41.600 --> 00:21:47.526
We have this treasure in earthen vessels, that the excellency of the power will be known of Him and not of us.

00:21:47.527 --> 00:21:55.599
And if you have the attitude that you have to be exalted in these last days, you are missing it. You're going to be left.

00:21:55.600 --> 00:22:05.541
And I'm telling you, woe unto you that have that kind of an attitude because He will not have His glory shared, ladies and gentlemen.

00:22:05.542 --> 00:22:14.158
It's about giving God glory in these last days. That's what He told me. He said, 'Brandon, always stay small in your own eyes.

00:22:14.159 --> 00:22:28.502
Never look for man's praise because just like they praised me going in, saying "Glory to Him in the highest,"and they were doing the palm branches and doing all the things that they were doing, they turned on me the next week and said, "Crucify Him!

00:22:28.503 --> 00:22:43.054
Crucify Him!"'Man's opinion will change like the weather, ladies and gentlemen, because we're all just messed up without Jesus.

00:22:43.055 --> 00:22:47.410
I'm not here for your praise. I'm not here for the comment section to give me a big hit.

00:22:47.411 --> 00:22:59.740
I'm here to say, 'Well done, thou good and faithful servant.'When I enter into my rest, when I get on the other side, my job is to tell you Jesus Christ is coming and He's coming soon.

00:22:59.741 --> 00:23:11.599
My job is to tell you, you better repent because Jesus is coming and there will be one last call and Jesus is coming for His bride.

00:23:11.600 --> 00:23:21.599
Are you ready today? Is your heart ready before Him? Do you understand that it's not about record deals and Dove Awards?

00:23:21.600 --> 00:23:28.749
That the anointed songs of the past were anointed because they had a heart just for Him.

00:23:28.750 --> 00:23:38.959
They didn't care about becoming viral. Who cares about being viral?

00:23:38.960 --> 00:23:43.147
My video went viral? I don't care. I hide in a hole. I don't care.

00:23:43.148 --> 00:23:52.319
They want to say, 'Well, you got 160 million hits and all this.'Who cares? Most of them were persecuting you anyway.

00:23:52.320 --> 00:24:03.592
But He said, 'The more they persecute you, the more I will increase the anointing on your life because if they loved you, Brandon, then you ain't of me.

00:24:03.593 --> 00:24:19.119
But if they hate you, they hated me. They hated me, son. So they're going to hate you.'How much more do I want His praise than anybody else's?

00:24:19.120 --> 00:24:28.969
If they hated Jesus, they're going to hate you. But if they love you, you better watch yourself because I want to be like Jesus.

00:24:28.970 --> 00:24:36.849
I want to be like Him. My goal every day is to wake up and say, 'Jesus, I want to be more like You.

00:24:36.850 --> 00:24:48.399
I want to be more like You—less and less of this world and more like Jesus.'If you have that heart, you're on the right road.

00:24:48.400 --> 00:24:55.523
But they're going to hate you and they're going to persecute you just like they persecute me.

00:24:55.524 --> 00:25:08.239
They run me down. They're evil people. But I say, 'God, thank you for the opportunity to be persecuted for Your name's sake.

00:25:08.240 --> 00:25:25.016
Thank you for the opportunity to be persecuted for Your name's sake.'If that's the least I could go through for You, for them to make fun of me, it was all for Your glory.

00:25:25.017 --> 00:25:38.565
That when I get on the other side, it's 'Well done, thou good and faithful servant. Enter into my rest.'People have no idea the persecution.

