The nights I have had here are just sitting there weeping, saying, 'God, the pressure is so intense.'But He comes and loves on me.

00:25:46.686 --> 00:25:50.857
And I want to sit at His feet and I want to bask in His presence.

00:25:50.858 --> 00:26:15.477
And I want to sit there and go, 'Oh.'Because when my praises go up, His blessings come down. I'm taken back by His love for me.

00:26:15.478 --> 00:26:30.043
I'm taken back at the visitations that I've had with Him even lately to warn you all about what's coming. A great shaking of America is coming to awaken.

00:26:30.044 --> 00:26:43.759
And in this shaking, He said, 'Never quote dates anymore.'And I want you to be very slow to speak and quick to pray.

00:26:43.760 --> 00:26:48.233
Spend more time praying and less time speaking on this channel.

00:26:48.234 --> 00:26:55.918
It should be an oasis for people to be refreshed for what's coming.

00:26:55.919 --> 00:27:01.278
They have got to learn how to drink and hear me for themselves.

00:27:01.279 --> 00:27:11.834
It is not about the prophetic anymore concerning saying, 'Well, I got to tell you.'I want you to learn how to drink yourself.

00:27:11.835 --> 00:27:19.359
You need to learn how to hear yourself for there may not be a YouTube soon.

00:27:19.360 --> 00:27:30.316
There may not be an internet soon. What would you do if all the prophetic voices were silent on YouTube?

00:27:30.317 --> 00:27:40.798
What would you do? Would you be lost? Or would you know how to cultivate it for yourself and get into those rivers and hear Him for you?

00:27:40.799 --> 00:27:48.158
Because in that, all the voices will be quiet and all you have is Him and you.

00:27:48.159 --> 00:27:56.274
That's where you need to be. Who cares? It's about you and Him.

00:27:56.275 --> 00:28:22.558
He said, 'Brandon, you don't need to tell them anymore about the financial crash—when, where, how.'He said, 'The crash is coming for the people and the things to shake them, to awaken them because they're not hearing me in the first place.'It's not so you can prepare them so they'll go buy their goods and all their stuff; it's so that they hear me for themselves.

00:28:22.559 --> 00:28:34.319
Their ears are closed to me. They've not known how to get into my word and flow in the gifts of the Spirit by praying in the Spirit because they're dry.

00:28:34.320 --> 00:28:43.199
You are helping them to stay dry. Tell them to fan their flame so they can find it for themselves.

00:28:43.200 --> 00:28:49.669
If you teach them to fish instead of giving them fish, they'll starve if you keep giving them the fish.

00:28:49.670 --> 00:28:56.239
But if I teach you to fish, you'll learn how to feed your whole family.

00:28:56.240 --> 00:29:07.119
The problem is that you do not know how to do it yourself. And you have got to learn how to hear Him for what's coming.

00:29:07.120 --> 00:29:15.125
Get yourself right before the Father. Take communion daily. It's not hard.

00:29:15.126 --> 00:29:23.519
You get your juice and your bread and you go before Him just like you do at church and say the exact same thing: 'Father, this is Your body.

00:29:23.520 --> 00:29:30.076
This is Your blood.'You don't have to make it all... He wants it to be just like what a child would do before Him.

00:29:30.077 --> 00:29:38.479
We don't have to be all hyper-super-religious. God does not like—He said He hates self-righteousness.

00:29:38.480 --> 00:29:42.878
He hates it. And He hates religion the way everybody else, the thees and thous, the Pharisees.

00:29:42.879 --> 00:29:48.983
We've got to go back to just being like a child. Be simple. Be simple.

00:29:48.984 --> 00:29:56.106
Our relationship with the Lord should be simple. It shouldn't be so complicated.

00:29:56.107 --> 00:30:02.688
It's not algebra. It's subtraction and addition. Simple math.

00:30:02.689 --> 00:30:11.808
Does that make sense? Simple math, not algebra or calculus or whatever. It's easy.

00:30:11.809 --> 00:30:17.077
We've made it so hard, but God said, 'Come to me like a child.'How does a child go?

00:30:17.078 --> 00:30:22.505
'I want to crawl up in your lap, Daddy. How you doing today? I want to tug on your garment, Dad.

00:30:22.506 --> 00:30:27.654
Hey, can I have an ice cream? Can I have a cookie? Hey, Daddy, I want to tell you I love you.'You have a little five-year-old.

00:30:27.655 --> 00:30:39.765
'I want to tell you I love you, Dad.'They're just begging for your time and attention. 'Can you play cars with me? Can you play cards with me?

00:30:39.766 --> 00:30:46.926
Can you play dollies with me?'They're never trying to make things real complicated.

